# Tic Tac Toe Game in Java

This is a simple Tic Tac Toe game implemented in Java using the Swing library for the graphical user interface (GUI). The game allows two players to play against each other on a 3x3 grid.

## Features

- Two-player gameplay (X and O)
- Win detection for rows, columns, and diagonals
- Draw detection when the board is full
- Simple and intuitive GUI

## Requirements

- Java Development Kit (JDK) 8 or higher
- An IDE or text editor (e.g., IntelliJ IDEA, Eclipse, or Visual Studio Code)

## Getting Started

### Clone the Repository

You can clone this repository using the following command:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/TicTacToe.git